| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

gcc-future
==========
gcc-future is a daily snapshot of the tip of the GCC development tree.

Setup
-----
You should add ${TRUEPREFIX}/gnu/bin to your $PATH.

Remove the /usr/lib/libstdc++* and /usr/lib/libsupc++* libraries.

Tips
----
For maximum compatibility with C++ libraries, add the -static-libstdc++
and -static-libgcc flags to your C++ linker invocations.
